data.text:
@IanHammar Hej! Jag rekommenderar att du sänder denna fråga till vår Investor Relations email så kanske de har möjlighet att svara dig, du hittar kontaktuppgifter på https://t.co/jBuntJzMgU

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@TheGrippers Hello! Sadly we don't have a SAS self-service baggage drop at Chania but please check with the airport when you get there as they may have a baggage drop during these times to decrease the check-in lines and wait time.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ValvdbVdb Hello! Please contact us via Messenger or live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking details and we will help you take a look at the voucher errand.

Best regards,
Anton.

@birkbeckRus Hello. I'm sorry to hear that the flight was delayed, to apply for compensation please open a claim with our Customer Care department at https://t.co/OzrIxYNv63 - make sure to attach receipts if you have any and Customer Care will contact you  by email.

Best regards,
Anton.

@MHerlman Hello, if your destination does not require a negative covid-19 test to enter then we will not require it to board the plane either. You can find the latest entry restrictions for your destination at https://t.co/oj06rsm5qG

Best regards,
Anton.

@HeathSusanAlder Hej! För att ansöka om återbetalning av en biljett kan du gå till https://t.co/DvYHoiTdFv eller kontakta kundtjänst, om du inte kommer fram via telefon så kan du prova Messenger eller Live-chatt istället.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@KarenLanza7 Hello! When traveling from one country to another with a continued domestic route in your destination country - the baggage has to be checked in again at the first stop in that country. So in this case you will have to check-in your baggage again in Oslo.

Best regards,
Anton

@YarnAddictAnni Hello, yes we do. You can find more information at https://t.co/E6bpHzaWLm under "Face mask requirements".

Best regards,
Anton.

@ingridod Hej Ingrid, vänligen kolla om du har någon VPN eller företagsbrandvägg igång som kan orsaka problem med hemsidan. Prova gärna också att rensa cache och cookies i din webbläsare för att se om det hjälper.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@PerWahlenius Hej! Om du fortfarande behöver komma i kontakt med vår Bagageservice på Arlanda så hittar du telefonnumret på https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@APxx77 Hello. I'm sorry to hear that you are still missing your refund from June last year. Please contact us via live-chat or phone with your booking details so we can investigate this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@KvonBeetzen Hi again, you can use this link to find the entry restrictions for your destination(s) https://t.co/oj06rsDGPg - it is connected to the IATA Timatic database with the latest information. We apologize for the late answer.

Best regards,
Anton.

@AiemanQuadar Hello! We do not fly between these countries sadly. Regarding the policy of who is allowed to travel or not is decided upon by the authorities of the countries you are traveling between and not the airlines themselves.

Best regards,
Anton.

@DavidRu88515295 Hi! I am sorry to hear that your baggage is delayed, unfortunately we are unable to help you with this over Twitter but I recommend you call our Baggage Service at EWR for more information https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@NauwelaersP Hello. I'm sorry to hear that you are dissatisfied with us, if you wish to send a complaint to us about your experience please use our feedback form https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@michelsagen Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your flight was cancelled. At the moment the queue at customer service is longer than usual and we apologize for the inconvenience it causes - all I can recommend for now is that you try to call us again.

Best regards,
Anton.

@tweetoeo Hello! All carry-on baggage must be within the size and weight limits and fit under the seat in front of you. Coats and jackets can be stowed in the overhead compartment.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Steneroes Hello, thank you for your feedback and we apologize for the longer than usual queue times that we have right now and the inconvenience that this is causing for our customers.

Best regards,
Anton.

@EricFussballer Hello, due to the current situation during the pandemic only the SAS HUB lounges are open. We apologize for the inconvenience but other lounges are closed until further notice.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Rikskelton Hello! It might take up to 2 weeks sometimes for the voucher to be issued, hopefully it won't take much longer before you receive your voucher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@KvonBeetzen Hello, we do not require covid-19 tests for Swedish passengers flying back to Sweden.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Yellowtroos When calling us to book a trip that is not possible online due to website limitations we will not charge the service fee.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ricogadedk Hello. At the moment our customer service queue times are longer than usual and we apologize for the inconvenience - Please just wait in the chat or phone line and you will be connected to an agent as soon as possible.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Jobbcoachen1 Hej! Tack för din feedback. Det stämmer att man inte behöver ha ansiktsmasken på sig när man äter eller dricker ombord på flyget - dock om någon av våra passagerare väljer att dricka läsk under hela resan så är det inget vi kan påverka tyvärr.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@jasonoruairc Hello, I'm sorry to hear that you are still waiting for your refund. Please contact us with your booking reference so we can investigate this, our contact info can be found at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@camillaley Hej! 

Jag beklagar att du upplevde det så, om du ringer vår kundtjänst och väntar kvar i telefon så kommer du hamna i kön efter några meddelanden. Våra agenter jobbar så hårt som möjligt för att svara på alla samtal.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@Yellowtroos Hi! 

Glad to hear that you were able to book your trip. It's sadly not possible to book a trip with points and a voucher online right now, so you need to call our customer service so they can help you have a look at it in that case.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Yellowtroos Hi! 

Yes it's possible to book a trip with points and a voucher but you have to call our customer service in that case. So it's sadly not possible to do it yourself online. You can find our contact info here: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R

//Best regards, Dennis.

@hertagoon Hej! 

Tyvärr kan vi inte garantera att kapaciteten ökas för augusti i det fallet, då det är så nära inpå.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@matiasmas12 Hi! 
To help speed up the boarding process and reduce the risk of cramped situations onboard SAS is for the time being limiting the number of allowed carry-on items to 1 per person. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@mariamir62 Hi, you can try to use this link to see if you can find out what is required for your transfer in CPH: https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De
If that doesn't help, you have all the travel restrictions airlines follow here: https://t.co/I5lXILKAf5 
Kind regards, Rebecka

@dancefortheworm Hi! 
Okay yes you should be able to find it on this page: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@PaaKorsgaarden Hej! 
Jo det ser ut som att det flyget vart inställt på grund av strejken på den flygplatsen. 

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@kendoesracing Hi! 
Okay yes arrival service needs to create a case for you at the airport, so i recommend that you call them as soon as possible so they can create it for you.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Ste_Forna Hi! 
Yes you will need to check in the luggage again at CPH if you are changing airlines. 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@PaaKorsgaarden Hej! 
Okej jag beklagar om ditt flyg vart inställt så nära inpå avgång, men i det fallet skulle jag rekommendera att du ringer vår kundtjänst så vi kan hjälpa dig kolla vidare på det.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@trineka Hej! 
Just nu har vi dessvärre inte några direktflyg ifrån CPH till Östersund, men om vi börjar med det så kommer vi lägga ut det på vår hemsida https://t.co/mI1PgdtR1y så fort som möjligt. 

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@kar_hansen Hi, There is unfortunately long queues to customer service for the moment, but we can not check booking references or status of refund here on twitter.

Regards,
Peter

@AnserGIS I recommend you create a delayed bag report here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 If you received a notification that your bag has arrived at the airport you are able to pick it up at the airport. https://t.co/gMhxX3iD1U
Your bag will otherwise be delivered asap
Kind regards, Rebecka

@LouisHuntley96 Hi, I am terribly sorry to hear that this happened. You can check the options available on our website to rebook or request a refund: https://t.co/Og0nmll5Op 
Please call our support if you need more assistance with your booking: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Rebecka

@kvzm5 Hi, we are terribly sorry that you missed your bag. If you received a notification that your bag has arrived at the airport you are able to pick it up at the airport. https://t.co/gMhxX3iD1U
Your bag will otherwise be delivered as soon as possible.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@BetinaFigen I recommend you create a delayed bag report here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 If you received a notification that your bag has arrived at the airport you are able to pick it up at the airport. https://t.co/gMhxX3iD1U
Your bag will otherwise be delivered asap
Kind regards, Rebecka

@PivoManBlog Hi PivoManBlog, Please contact us at Customer Service at the following link, or over Facebook Messenger and we will look in to your errand,
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Isak

@halalyeen Hi Halalyeen, Right now the Hand Luggage is restricted to 1 bag for each passenger, You can read more information regarding this matter at the following link under "Changes to our services" and "Carry-on"
https://t.co/gml5ZaEizi

Kind regards, Isak

@AnserGIS Hi AnserGIS, You can find contact information to our baggage support at the following link, please contact the airport where you landed.
https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Kind regards, Isak

@jawst97 Hi
You can request refund after 12 months have passed. The voucher does not need to be expired.
Kind regards /Anna

@shawnallenlive Hi Shawn
Contact us on live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or messenger with your booking reference and we will help you.
Kind regards /Anna
